7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Process Street and Relay.app share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Api Connections, Scheduling, Conditional Logic. On the other hand, Relay.app uniquely offers Error Handling, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Process Street holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Relay.app scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Relay.app comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Process Street begins at $100/mo. Relay.app stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Process Street requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
